<A>__{down in the ballroom, jo is looking up anxiously as she sings. she deliberately breaks and pauses for a moment and softens her accompaniment. then she hears it a faint whistle coming from above, not enough for those around to appreciate it, but loud enough for the straining ears of jo. she looks across the ballroom to find ben, and her eyes go up.}
<L>__{interior embassy (night) medium close shot}
<A>__{watching her, ben understands. he gives her the slightest sign of agreement.}
